<h1>Actions</h1>
<%- if @message -%>
<p class="msg"><%= h(@message) %></p>
<%- end -%>
<p class="lead">Every action runs through the same lock as scheduled runs — a click can never
start a second concurrent pipeline. Long actions run in the background; results appear in the
<a href="#jobs">job list</a> below. Restores are CLI-only by design.</p>

<div class="action-grid">
  <form class="action-card" method="post" action="/actions/backup">
    <div class="action-head">
      <span class="action-icon accent">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="8" ry="3"/><path d="M4 5v6c0 1.7 3.6 3 8 3s8-1.3 8-3V5"/><path d="M4 11v6c0 1.7 3.6 3 8 3"/><path d="M17 21v-6m0 0-2.5 2.5M17 15l2.5 2.5"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <h3>Back up now</h3>
        <p>Run the full dump → compress → encrypt → fan-out pipeline.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= h(@csrf_token) %>">
    <div class="field">
      <label class="field-label" for="backup-db">Database</label>
      <select id="backup-db" name="database">
        <option value="">All databases</option>
        <%- @database_names.each do |name| -%>
        <option value="<%= h(name) %>"><%= h(name) %></option>
        <%- end -%>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <span class="field-label">Destinations <span class="muted">— none selected fans out to all</span></span>
      <div class="chip-set">
        <%- @destinations.each do |dest| -%>
        <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" name="destinations[]" value="<%= h(dest.token) %>"><span><%= h(dest.label) %></span></label>
        <%- end -%>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="action-foot">
      <label class="switch"><input type="checkbox" name="confirm"><span class="slider"></span><span class="switch-label">Confirm</span></label>
      <button type="submit">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg>
        Back up
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <form class="action-card" method="post" action="/actions/verify">
    <div class="action-head">
      <span class="action-icon ok">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 3 5 6v5c0 4.5 3 7.5 7 9 4-1.5 7-4.5 7-9V6l-7-3Z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <h3>Verify latest backups</h3>
        <p>Tier 1 checksum + Tier 2 structural check; deep restores into a scratch database.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= h(@csrf_token) %>">
    <div class="field">
      <span class="field-label">Depth</span>
      <div class="chip-set">
        <label class="chip"><input type="checkbox" name="deep"><span>Deep — Tier 3 scratch-restore</span></label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="action-foot">
      <label class="switch"><input type="checkbox" name="confirm"><span class="slider"></span><span class="switch-label">Confirm</span></label>
      <button type="submit">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3 5 6v5c0 4.5 3 7.5 7 9 4-1.5 7-4.5 7-9V6l-7-3Z"/></svg>
        Verify
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <form class="action-card" method="post" action="/actions/prune">
    <div class="action-head">
      <span class="action-icon warn">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M4 7h16"/><path d="M9 7V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v2"/><path d="M6 7l1 12a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h8a1 1 0 0 0 1-1l1-12"/><path d="M10 11v6M14 11v6"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <h3>Prune</h3>
        <p>Enforce the retention policy. Dry run unless “apply” is on; the safety rails always hold.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= h(@csrf_token) %>">
    <div class="field">
      <span class="field-label">Mode</span>
      <div class="chip-set">
        <label class="chip danger"><input type="checkbox" name="apply"><span>Apply — actually delete</span></label>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="action-foot">
      <label class="switch danger"><input type="checkbox" name="confirm"><span class="slider"></span><span class="switch-label">Confirm</span></label>
      <button type="submit" class="danger">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 7h16M6 7l1 12a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h8a1 1 0 0 0 1-1l1-12M10 11v6M14 11v6"/></svg>
        Prune
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <form class="action-card" method="post" action="/actions/test-notification">
    <div class="action-head">
      <span class="action-icon accent">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M18 8a6 6 0 1 0-12 0c0 7-3 8-3 8h18s-3-1-3-8"/><path d="M10.5 20a2 2 0 0 0 3 0"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <h3>Send a test notification</h3>
        <p>Dispatch a test summary through every configured notifier.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= h(@csrf_token) %>">
    <div class="action-foot">
      <label class="switch"><input type="checkbox" name="confirm"><span class="slider"></span><span class="switch-label">Confirm</span></label>
      <button type="submit">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m4 4 16 8-16 8 4-8-4-8Z"/><path d="M8 12h8"/></svg>
        Send test
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <form class="action-card" method="post" action="/actions/doctor">
    <div class="action-head">
      <span class="action-icon accent">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M3 12h4l2 6 4-12 2 6h6"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <h3>Run doctor</h3>
        <p>Re-check tools, config, storage destinations, and database connectivity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= h(@csrf_token) %>">
    <div class="action-foot">
      <label class="switch"><input type="checkbox" name="confirm"><span class="slider"></span><span class="switch-label">Confirm</span></label>
      <button type="submit">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 12h4l2 6 4-12 2 6h6"/></svg>
        Doctor
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

<div class="panel">
  <div class="panel-head">
    <h2>Trigger remotely</h2>
    <p class="muted">Kick off the same actions from a script, webhook, cron on another host, or a phone
    shortcut. Authenticate with a dashboard token as a Bearer credential; the call returns a job id
    you can poll. Requires a <span class="mono">web.auth.token</span> or a
    <span class="mono">web.auth.tokens</span> entry (browser basic-auth can't reach these endpoints).
    Issue one token per caller so each can be revoked on its own.</p>
  </div>
  <pre class="mono"># Back up one database to just the NAS and Google Drive:
curl -sS -X POST https://HOST/api/actions/backup \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $PGKEEPER_WEB_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"database":"app_production","destinations":["nas","gdrive"]}'

# Poll the job it returned, or list recent jobs:
curl -sS https://HOST/api/jobs/1     -H "Authorization: Bearer $PGKEEPER_WEB_TOKEN"
curl -sS https://HOST/api/jobs        -H "Authorization: Bearer $PGKEEPER_WEB_TOKEN"
curl -sS https://HOST/api/destinations -H "Authorization: Bearer $PGKEEPER_WEB_TOKEN"</pre>
</div>

<h2 id="jobs">Jobs</h2>
<%- if @jobs.empty? -%>
<p class="muted">No jobs yet.</p>
<%- else -%>
<table>
  <tr><th>#</th><th>Action</th><th>Status</th><th>Started</th><th>Finished</th><th>Detail</th></tr>
  <%- @jobs.each do |job| -%>
  <tr>
    <td><%= job.id %></td>
    <td class="mono"><%= h(job.action) %></td>
    <td><%= pill(job.status, { running: 'warn', done: 'ok', failed: 'bad' }.fetch(job.status, '')) %></td>
    <td><%= h(fmt_time(job.started_at)) %></td>
    <td><%= job.finished_at ? h(fmt_time(job.finished_at)) : "-" %></td>
    <td><%= h(job.detail || "") %></td>
  </tr>
  <%- end -%>
</table>
<%- if @jobs.any?(&:running?) -%>
<p class="muted">A job is running — this page refreshes automatically.</p>
<script>setTimeout(function () { location.reload(); }, 4000);</script>
<%- else -%>
<p class="muted">Refresh the page to see new job results.</p>
<%- end -%>
<%- end -%>
